---
title: Chipotle BBQ Bacon and Bean Chilli Jacky-P with Cheese, Soured Cream and Slaw
description: Jacket potatoes aren't just for baked beans and cheese. Our Chipotle BBQ Bean Chilli Jacky-P is a smoky, Tex-Mex inspired twist on the humble jacket potato for a comforting weeknight dinner.
